WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.100 --> 00:00:03.666
Mingyu must be safe.

2
00:00:03.666 --> 00:00:04.766
He lives in the palace.

3
00:00:04.766 --> 00:00:06.666
The Empress wants him dead at her fingertips.

4
00:00:06.666 --> 00:00:08.366
You must listen to my sister.

5
00:00:08.566 --> 00:00:10.833
You're so nervous, do you like him?

6
00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:13.966
It's none of your business.

7
00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:17.900
You're still so considerate.

8
00:00:17.900 --> 00:00:19.133
Quite fickle, aren't you?

9
00:00:19.133 --> 00:00:19.933
Hmm.

10
00:00:20.966 --> 00:00:21.900
Madam.

11
00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:25.666
Cover your face when you talk to me in the future.

12
00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:29.200
I must have been blind to think he's my husband.

13
00:00:29.200 --> 00:00:31.800
He looks like someone but is double-faced.

14
00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:33.000
Yang in the wind, Yin in the text.

15
00:00:35.733 --> 00:00:37.033
Just consider me heartbroken.

16
00:00:38.366 --> 00:00:40.433
Nangong looks at him differently.

17
00:00:40.733 --> 00:00:43.400
Could it be he genuinely cares for him?
